<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using Zend_Config_Xml, and passing a none existing file to the constructor, you will get a fatal error: "PHP Fatal error:  Class 'Zend_Config_Xml' not found in ..."</p>

<p>How to reproduce:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
set_include_path('library');

require_once 'Zend/Config/Ini.php';
$config = new Zend_Config_Xml('foobazbar');
</code></pre>

<p>The condition on line 67 to 69 is missing the require_once 'Zend/Config/Exception.php';</p>

